  "title": "Prime Mover Driver (Container Trucking/ Loose Cargo) #62587",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Transportation/ Logistics</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Prime Mover Driver (Container Trucking) / Prime Mover Driver (Loose Cargo)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Tuas (Walk distance from MRT)</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 Days, Mon – Fri (8:30AM - 5:30PM), Sat (8:30AM -12:30PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + OT + Trip Incentive + Attendance Incentive (up to $5,000+)</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Safely transport containers or loose cargo between designated locations.</li><li>Conduct container trucking operations into yards.</li><li>Familiar with PSA operations and procedures.</li><li>Ensure the safety of both cargo and vehicle through regular checks and adherence to safety protocols.</li><li>Reporting any issues to Supervisor as they arise.</li><li>Other duties as required.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Must have Singapore Class 4/ 5 driving license.</li><li>At least 2 years' experience as a Prime Mover Driver in Singapore</li><li>Follow Singapore traffic regulations and PSA/ Jurong Port requirements.</li><li>Able and willing to start work early based on job needs.</li><li>Clean driving records.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#62587 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
